## Interface: 11508
## Title: LibCodex-1.0-CustomizationChoices
## Notes: Bundled seed data for LibCodex-1.0 / CustomizationChoices (Vanilla / Hardcore flavor). LoadOnDemand: LibCodex-1.0 auto-loads this on first :Get() miss against the CustomizationChoices module. Per-module split keeps the core lib's bytecode pool tiny and lets consumers pay only for modules they query.
## Author: ChronicTinkerer
## Version: 9
## LoadOnDemand: 1
## Dependencies: LibCodex-1.0
## X-Curse-Project-ID: 1532131
