# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# CustomizationChoices catalog for the Vanilla / Hardcore flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against CustomizationChoices.

Data_Vanilla\CustomizationChoices.lua
